      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, but my doctor is out of the office today and i can't really wait until monday to deal with this. it's just a regular headache, not like anything crazy. is it really that big of a deal for just one or two pills? i feel like i can manage it so i don't have to call the office immediately.",
